.TH GUESSGAME 1 "March 2026" "GuessGame 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
guessgame \- a fun terminal number-guessing game
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B guessgame
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B GuessGame
is a simple interactive game where the computer picks a secret number
between 1 and 100 and you try to guess it. It supports unlimited rounds
and gives helpful "too high / too low" feedback.
.SH OPTIONS
None. Just run it!
.SH AUTHOR
Created for LFCS practice on Ubuntu 24.04
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR printf (3)
.SH BUGS
Report bugs to your terminal window.
